
usage: getcon.pl <lnd.all file list> <bin_size> <extend_bin_num> <out_file>

lnd.all file list: one all file one line, see the test.list for example

bin_size: bin size used in the pipleine

extend_bin_num: as the merge1 parameter in the pipeline

the last four columns of out_file are the counts for RL, LR, LL, RR connections, please select the line depends on your own requests as the control list(by count or ratio).
for example, we select the lines with total counts over 5.
